import React from 'react'

function Dropdown() {
  return (
    <label>
        What do we eat?
        <select>
            <option value="fruit">Fruit</option>
            <option value="vegetable">Vegetable</option>
            <option value="meat">Meat</option>
        </select>
    </label>
  )
}

export default Dropdown
